---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Brickell Eight | Coming Soon</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Brickell Eight — Only Eight. Designed for the Few. Exclusive collection of eight contemporary residences moments from Brickell." />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="topbar">
			<div class="nav">
				<div class="nav-logo">
					<img src="/brickell-logo.jpg" alt="Brickell Eight Logo" />
					<div class="nav-title">Brickell Eight • Coming Soon</div>
				</div>
				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="#residences">Residences</a>
					<a href="#sales">Sales Team</a>
					<a href="https://brickelleight.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">brickelleight.com</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<main class="container">
			<section class="hero">
				<div class="panel hero-copy">
					<div class="eyebrow">Now Previewing</div>
					<h1>BRICKELL</h1>
					<div class="subbrand">EIGHT</div>
					<div class="tagline">Only Eight. Designed for the Few.</div>
					<p class="lead">
						An exclusive collection of eight contemporary residences moments from Brickell,
						crafted for buyers who value privacy, modern design, and a boutique Miami lifestyle.
					</p>

					<div class="meta">
						<div class="chip">8 Contemporary Residences</div>
						<div class="chip">Minutes from Brickell</div>
						<div class="chip">Exclusive Sales & Marketing</div>
					</div>

					<div class="cta">
						<a class="button" href="#sales">Contact Sales Team</a>
						<a class="button secondary" href="https://brickelleight.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit Website</a>
					</div>

					<div class="domain">brickelleight.com</div>
				</div>

				<div class="panel hero-media">
					<img src="/hero-image.jpg" alt="Brickell Eight Building" />
					<div class="media-card">
						<h3>Boutique scale. Refined presence.</h3>
						<p>
							A rare opportunity to present a limited eight-residence offering with clean contemporary architecture,
							private garage access, and a highly connected urban location.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="section" id="residences">
				<div class="section-grid">
					<div class="panel info-card">
						<h2>A Distinctive New Address</h2>
						<p>
							Brickell Eight combines an intimate scale, modern architecture, and an elevated residential
							lifestyle in the heart of Miami’s vibrant Brickell district. Designed with elegance and
							carefully considered proportions, the project offers a sense of privacy and sophistication
							that sets it apart from larger developments.
						</p>
						<p>
							Its architecture and interiors reflect understated luxury through the use of
							high-quality materials, natural stone textures, and a refined palette of soft pastel
							tones complemented by champagne-toned metallic accents, creating a timeless and
							elegant aesthetic. Expansive windows and open layouts enhance natural light and
							spaciousness within each residence.
						</p>
						<p>
							Located in one of Miami’s most dynamic neighborhoods, Brickell Eight places
							residents just steps from world-class dining, shopping, cultural venues, and the
							financial district, offering the perfect balance between exclusivity and urban
							living.
						</p>
						<div class="stats">
							<div class="stat">
								<strong>8</strong>
								<span>Residences</span>
							</div>
							<div class="stat">
								<strong>305</strong>
								<span>Miami Access</span>
							</div>
							<div class="stat">
								<strong>Now</strong>
								<span>Private Inquiry</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="panel hero-media">
						<img src="/gallery-1.jpg" alt="Brickell Eight Interior" />
						<!-- <img src="/gallery-2.jpg" alt="Brickell Eight View" /> -->
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="sales" id="sales">
				<div class="panel sales-card">
					<div class="sales-top">
						<div>
							<h2>Exclusive Sales & Marketing</h2>
							<p style="font-size:20px; line-height:1.6; margin:0 0 12px;">
								Presented with the same elegant visual language as your printed collateral,
								this page keeps the message simple, premium, and conversion-ready.
							</p>
							<p style="font-size:20px; line-height:1.6; margin:0;">
								Reach out directly to schedule a private conversation, request availability,
								or learn more about this exclusive collection.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="sales-flyer">
							<img src="/sales-flyer.jpg" alt="Brickell Eight Sales Flyer" />
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="brokers">
						<div class="broker">
							<div class="label">Exclusive Representative</div>
							<h3>Sebastian Acosta</h3>
							<a href="tel:+13052446222">305.244.6222</a>
							<small>Global Real Estate Advisor</small>
						</div>

						<div class="broker">
							<div class="label">Exclusive Representative</div>
							<h3>Rosi Borroto</h3>
							<a href="tel:+13054908176">305.490.8176</a>
							<small>Global Real Estate Advisor</small>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="brokerage">
						Exclusive Sales & Marketing<br />
						<strong>ONE Sotheby's International Realty</strong>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<footer>
			Brickell Eight • Coming Soon • Luxury residences moments from Brickell
		</footer>
	</body>
</html>
